    <item>
      <title>中国将弹药用金属列入限制出口清单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/china-adds-metal-used-in-ammo-to-list-of-restricted-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在加强对全球关键矿产供应的控制，对锑实施出口管制。锑是一种广泛用于弹药和其他军事用途的金属，今年价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/china-adds-metal-used-in-ammo-to-list-of-restricted-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 11:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
